{"tid":645722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<又贏？>中國軍機闖南韓防空識別區逗留約四小時 南韓出動F-15K戰鬥機監視","createTime":"2018-04-28T12:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T12:27:44.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"13dfa1df59bbc02fdaa70431ba47039d6f8ecb93","tid":645722,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:01:20.000Z","msg":"中國軍機闖韓防空識別區 南韓出動F-15K戰鬥機監視<br />\n<br />\n2018-04-28<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕南韓軍方指出，中國一架軍事飛機今日在未通報的情況下，飛入南韓防空識別區。<br />\n<br />\n根據《韓聯社》報導，南韓聯合參謀本部說明，一架中國偵察機，在今日上午10點44分從蘇岩礁西北方進入防空識別區，逗留約4個小時。<br />\n<br />\n參謀本部表示，該架軍機在靠近港口城市浦項市時轉向，朝東邊的郁陵島飛去，並在下午2點33分循著原路線離開識別區。<br />\n<br />\n南韓軍方不敢大意，出動包括F-15K等戰鬥機伴飛。當局也直接向北京政府溝通，強調任何增加緊張情勢的舉動，都有可能導致意外衝突。中方則表示，他們是在符合國際法的情況下，於國際領空進行正常訓練。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2409614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2409614&d=7n3VMjlbX0LGK%2BTf8D1p7ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=0b5b9c2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2409614&h=26a17b44\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2409614</a>"},{"pid":"6f5c1fa4daa2c6ead2979bd7b0123e3dfcdb4212","tid":645722,"uid":29804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:12:44.000Z","msg":"不甘寂寞"},{"pid":"13dece99762887196fb66c33cf863af6613b91f7","tid":645722,"uid":4239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:14:11.000Z","msg":"中方則表示，他們是在符合國際法的情況下，於國際領空進行正常訓練。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b896c8dc4dd98623c74bca864d2bfebe84e5e544","tid":645722,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88545ba8ee1bddc52bd761758307bcc9ea98c445","tid":645722,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:23:13.000Z","msg":"出黎拎存在感"},{"p